===Noun=== 
'''bacteria'''

#Plural of [[bacterium]].
#A derisive term for a lowlife or a slob (could be treated as plural or singular).

====Usage note====
*This is the plural form of the word.  While it is often used as if it were singular (as a collective noun), this is incorrect.  See the examples of correct usage under ''[[bacterium]]''.

